It tells so much about the interviewees how do they have their wings, I'm thinking about taking this show and use it as a dating filter!



Many of the interviewees just take a tiny little a bite, even trying to avoid the extra spice they themselves added to the wing, so they just act like they play it cool, but in fact they are posers and just lie the whole time (e.g. Matty Matheson or this woman here).


Some of them however are *honest*, they have it full, they let it on and are commited, bring it on baby! - and I like those characters so much! They are *real*! Coolio, Shia LaBeouf or Halle Berry for example, just to mention a few, from the top of my head.


I learn more about these people from their gestures and the way they eat & react to hot sauces, than from the questions they answer! Man I LOVE this show! Keep it coming!
